headlines.description: — Scottie Barnes scored 33 points, Immanuel Quickley added 23 and the Toronto Raptors snapped a four-game losing streak with a 106-103 victory over the Philadelphia 76ers on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Raptors drop 76ers to a season-worst 13 games under .500 with 106-103 victory

events.name: New York Knicks at Indiana Pacers

headlines.description: — Karl-Anthony Towns had 40 points and 12 rebounds, Josh Hart added 30 points and 10 rebounds and the New York Knicks beat the Indiana Pacers 128-115 on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Karl-Anthony Towns scores 40 and Josh Hart has 30 to lead Knicks past Pacers 128-115

headlines.description: — Ja Morant scored 26 points, Desmond Bane had 20 and the Memphis Grizzlies held on to beat the Phoenix Suns 119-112 on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ja Morant scores 26 and the Grizzlies hold on late to beat Durant and the Suns 119-112
